title: Digital-Tutors - Creating Compelling Environment Concepts in Pho
description:
Digital-Tutors - Creating Compelling Environment Concepts in Photoshop
======================================================================
English | AVC 1280x720 15 fps | AAC 128 Kbps 44.1 KHz | 1.22 GB
Genre: eLearning | Level: Advanced
------             ------


In this tutorial, we learn how to paint an environment in Photoshop.

Throughout these lessons we will learn how to combine stock photos and painting techniques to create a compelling environment concept. We will go through all the phases of the design and creation process. Lighting, composition, depth, and scale are just a few of the many fundamental aspects we will go through.

By the end you'll have a better understand of quality digital painting and how to do it fast and efficient.
